This paper is primarily focused on measuring and improving mobile network performance, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the challenges of implementing the measurement method and the analysis of the collected data, which could be categorized under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), social and information networks (cs.SI), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
